  "texts": [
    "This finding underscores the potential performance enhancement that transfer learning can offer by leveraging pre-trained models and adapting them to specific tasks.",
    "PTM helps the user avoid messing with hyper-parameters.",
    "Likewise, the PTM's initial layers are viewed as feature descriptors, extracting low-level features, including shades, blobs, edges, textures, and tints, and the target model may only need to re-train the PTM's last few layers because we believe the last few layers carry out the complicated tasks.",
    "Results of ExperimentsExperimental studies and additional evaluations are discussed.",
    "Firstly, we present the datasets and then the implementation details."
